/// It expands to `fsw` `rs2, offset(x2)`.
///
/// # Forms
/// Assembly: `c.fswsp fs2, imm(sp)`
/// Rust: `c_fswsp(rs2, imm)`
///
/// # Arguments
/// - `rs2` — Instruction operand.
