/// h! Maximum valid input (after rounding) ! `2^31 - 1`
/// h! Output for out-of-range negative input ! `-2^31`
/// h! Output for `-&infin;` ! `-2^31`
/// h! Output for out-of-range positive input ! `2^31 - 1`
/// h! Output for `+&infin;` for `NaN` ! `2^31 - 1`
/// !===
